ch.nolix.common.container

Class List<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.nolix.common.container.List<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IContainer<E>, Clearable, java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public class List<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IContainer<E>
    A list is a container that can add elements at the begin or at the end.
